claim: See Figure 1 for plot of mediation effects.
title: Figure 1.
caption:
Mediation of Family and Peer Functioning on Association Between Pandemic Impacts and Child Mental Health Symptomatology.
Note: Sex and age modifiers not displayed in this view. Values presented in this figure are written as effect coefficient (standard error). P values are indicated as follows: *** = p≤.001, **= p≤.01, * = p≤.05
Abbreviations: Pandemic impacts= Coronavirus Impact Scale, EDI = Emotion Dysregulation Index
